# Slider — Styles

## Class structure
- `.acko-slider` — flex column, `width: 100%`, `user-select: none`
- `.acko-slider-track` — relative container, `cursor: pointer`, `touch-action: none`, contains fill + thumb
- `.acko-slider-fill` — absolute, left-anchored, `background: var(--color-primary)`, `border-radius: var(--radius-full)`
- `.acko-slider-thumb` — absolute, `transform: translateX(-50%)`, bordered circle, `cursor: grab`
- `.acko-slider-ticks` — tick mark row beneath track
- `.acko-slider-tick` — `width/height: var(--scale-2)`, `background: var(--color-border-subtle)`
- `.acko-slider-tick-filled` — `background: var(--color-primary)`
- `.acko-slider-value` — right-aligned numeric label

## Size classes
| Class | Track height | Thumb size |
|-------|-------------|-----------|
| `.acko-slider-sm` | `var(--scale-4)` | `var(--scale-16)` |
| `.acko-slider-md` | `var(--scale-6)` | `var(--scale-20)` |
| `.acko-slider-lg` | `var(--scale-8)` | `var(--scale-24)` |

## States
- Track base: `background: var(--color-border-subtle)`
- Fill: `background: var(--color-primary)`
- Thumb hover: `box-shadow: var(--shadow-md), 0 0 0 var(--scale-4) var(--color-primary-ring)`
- Thumb focus-visible: `box-shadow: var(--shadow-focus-ring)`
- Thumb active: `cursor: grabbing; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1.1)`
- Disabled: `opacity: 0.45`, `pointer-events: none`; fill/thumb use `--color-text-disabled`
